## slu jwt parse

Parse JWT from stdin into JSON list of 3 objects (Header, Payload, Signature)

```
slu jwt parse <jwt> [flags]
```

### Options

```
  -f, --format-dates   Format dates from UNIX to local date-time
  -h, --help           help for parse
```
